@page
@* @model Exclousive.Models.AboutViewModel *@

<h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-center mb-6">About Us</h1>

<div class="w-full mx-auto p-4">
  <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Welcome to Exclousive! We are dedicated to providing you with the best selection of products, focusing on quality
    and customer satisfaction. Our mission is to offer a seamless shopping experience that meets your needs and exceeds
    your expectations.
  </p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Our Story</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    Exclousive started with a passion for delivering premium products to our customers. Our journey began in [Year], and
    since then, we have grown into a trusted name in the industry, known for our commitment to excellence and
    innovation.
  </p>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">What We Offer</h2>
  <ul class="list-disc list-inside mb-4 text-gray-700">
    <li>High-quality products sourced from trusted manufacturers</li>
    <li>Exceptional customer service and support</li>
    <li>Easy and secure online shopping experience</li>
    <li>Regular updates and promotions for our valued customers</li>
  </ul>
  <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Get in Touch</h2>
  <p class="text-gray-700 mb-4">
    We love to hear from you! If you have any questions or feedback, feel free to contact us through our <a
      href="@Url.Action("Contact", "Home")" class="text-blue-500 hover:underline">Contact Page</a>.
  </p>
</div>
